Russia Has Resources to Weather Difficult Markets, Shuvalov Says

-- B y   L y u b o v   P r o n i n a
-- 
2011-09-25T08:20:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/russia-has-resources-to-weather-difficult-markets-shuvalov-says.html
Russia has sufficient financial
resources to weather challenges arising from “very difficult”
global market conditions that are expected in the coming years,
First Deputy Prime Minister  Igor Shuvalov  said.  Russia has sufficient financial resources to respond to the
challenges, Shuvalov said today at a United Russia congress in
Moscow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lyubov Pronina in Moscow at 
 lpronina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
